subscription terms and conditions; 
(d) a detailed description of the rights and obligations attached to the crypto -assets 
and the procedures and conditions for exercising those rights; 
(e) information on the underlying technology and  standards applied by the issuer 
of the crypto -assets allowing for the holding, storing and transfer of those 
crypto-assets; 
(f) a detailed description of the risks relating to the issuer of the crypto -assets, the 
crypto-assets, the offer to the public of the crypto-asset and the implementation 
of the project; 
(g) the disclosure items specified in Annex I. 
